            <div class="text-praxis-dark-blue text-3xl mb-4">üîí</div>
            <h3 class="h6 text-praxis-dark-blue mb-3">SOC2 Type II Report</h3>
            <p class="body-base text-praxis-gray-600 mb-4">
              Audited security and availability controls report from independent
              third-party assessor.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="body-small text-praxis-gray-500">PDF ‚Ä¢ 1.8 MB</span>
              <a
                href="mailto:compliance@praxisnavigator.io?subject=SOC2 Report Request"
